I"‚<h2 id="about">About</h2>

<p>Monochrome is a minimal, responsive, ready to use Jekyll theme for
blogging.</p>

<h2 id="features">Features</h2>

<ul>
  <li>Completely responsive and mobile first</li>
  <li>Clean SEO friendly URLs, auto-generated from post title (no messy dates in the url)</li>
  <li>SEO title/description integration</li>
  <li>Sitemap ready</li>
  <li>Pagination support</li>
  <li>Mobile friendly navigation menu</li>
  <li>Easy customization for header, footer, navigation links, colors, favicon etc</li>
  <li>Default Monochrome Color Palette - black, white, greys</li>
  <li>About page</li>
  <li>404 page</li>
  <li>..and a lot more</li>
</ul>

